	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well this is from a 53 wizard so not uber or anything but at my level, my base int of 142 gives me a 1611.2 mana which is about 11.3 mana a point, from gear the ratio is about 10.6 mana per point.&nbsp;&nbsp;So at this level your are basically losing 22.4 mana from the difference, not as dramatic as 600 point difference you are worried about, just means that you will have to buy more gear than some of us others.  After 200 the ratio decreases significantly so doesn't hurt your pool as bad.  Hope this helped out a little bit.  Happy hunting.<br>&nbsp;<br>Brodicius <br>53 Wizard<br>unguilded<br>Tunare</td></tr>
