	   <tr><td colspan=2>this is very simple i will name 3 options you can do.&nbsp;&nbsp;i will discuss clerics wizards and chanters.  first off wizards are very strong nukers but you will be sitting down alot because they are basically mana only chars.  they can root which is effective for soloing.  chanters are better for groups then soloing but can solo farely easy.  you can make lots of money at high lvls if you start selling kei.  the pet can be frstrating but its only there to serve as a distraction.  if your pet dies though better mezz and run.  now clerics are sorda the bards of casters.  they can solo they can group and they can duel quite effectivly.  they get decent DD magic spells along with root and fear spells.  they also get Undead only nukes and DoTS.  there buffs are the best in the game.  if you want alot of solo action or group action these all work good.  if you would rather have a decent amount of hp and ac then get a cleric.  if you would rather kite stuff and run around alot be a wizard.  and if you would like to make alot of money at lvl 60 and be a great asset to a group do a chanter.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
